Yes.

55
00:07:46,549 --> 00:07:49,177
You don't talk much.

56
00:07:51,221 --> 00:07:52,973
Not really.

57
00:08:57,287 --> 00:08:58,288
It's over there.

58
00:09:08,256 --> 00:09:09,599
It's dangerous.

59
00:09:12,802 --> 00:09:14,600
No, it's not. You can come.

60
00:09:21,978 --> 00:09:23,776
Let's go to the camp.

61
00:09:24,939 --> 00:09:26,782
Across this lake?

62
00:09:27,776 --> 00:09:29,278
