00:28:49,478 --> 00:28:52,027
He seems to be calmer.

175
00:28:54,274 --> 00:28:56,117
How was it there?

176
00:28:56,443 --> 00:28:58,445
Okay.

177
00:28:58,946 --> 00:29:01,790
