00:29:10,999 --> 00:29:13,468
It's different, really.

182
00:29:14,169 --> 00:29:15,842
What's so different?

183
00:29:19,174 --> 00:29:20,391
It's just...

184
00:29:22,427 --> 00:29:23,849
different.

185
00:29:34,940 --> 00:29:38,285
