537
01:12:02,777 --> 01:12:03,903
Curious.

538
01:12:05,780 --> 01:12:08,078
She looks good, right?
Yoo-rim.

539
01:12:09,367 --> 01:12:11,040
You do, too.

540
01:12:13,120 --> 01:12:16,044
