light in the room.

786
01:40:01,204 --> 01:40:02,376
That's true

787
01:40:09,754 --> 01:40:10,471
Coffee?

788
01:40:10,463 --> 01:40:12,761
Yeah, let's get some
pulla as well.

789
01:40:29,815 --> 01:40:31,032
Watch out.

790
01:41:33,671 --> 01:41:35,844
How are you?
How many people?

791
01:41:38,509 --> 01:41:39,761
Ah.. Where is the toilet?

792
01:41:39,760 --> 01:41:41,888
Toilet? Just around
the corner over there.

793
01:41:48,144 --> 01:41:49,316
Give me a bite.

794
01:43:43,509 --> 01:43:44,681
Hello.

795
01:43:45,678 --> 01:43:46,850
<i>It's me.</i>

796
01:43:48,472 --> 01:43:49,644
Yes.

797
01:43:50,683 --> 01:43:52,936
<i>Hello? Sang-min?</i>

798
01:43:53,853 --> 01:43:55,355
I'm listening.

799
01:43:56,522 --> 01:43:59,366
<i>I can't hear you clearly.
Hello?</i>

800
01:43:59,859 --> 01:44:01,361
<i>Do you hear me well?</i>

801
01:44:01,360 --> 01:44:03,613
